Monolepta yasumatsui
Kimoto, 1969: 51 (Nantou, Ilan); 
Kimoto 1991
: 15 (Kaohsiung); 
Kimoto and Chu 1996
: 83 (catalogue); 
Kimoto and Takizawa 1997
